author: Marko Robnik-Sikonja and Igor Kononenko
title: Pruning Regression Trees with MDL
window: each consisting of 10 attributes - 2, 3 or 4 important, the rest are random, and containing 1000 examples. UCI datasets used were: Abalone predicting the age of the abalone, 1 nominal and 7 continuous attributes, 4177 instances. Autompg: city-cycle fuel consumption, 1 nominal, 6 continuous attributes 398 instances.
